text: Dhanashree Deshpande - Ganatra (born 2 February 1970 in Khopoli, Maharashtra) is an Indian musician. She is best known for her musical variety show You, Me and Chai, which has been performed live across Maharashtra since 2013. She is also known for her book of devotional poetry Dhanu Dnyaniyachi (2016). She has composed music for the films Tikli and Laxmi Bomb (2017), and Bayko Deta Ki Bayko (2020). She has also produced songs for singers Arya Ambekar and Aditya Mahajan, and sang on an album with Rahul Deshpande. == References == Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Indian musicians
